{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775893685938,"sessionID":"ses_2847f2e74ffeGWPWz8Ke9vbXmV","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8318290017CAzxNzNSV35yh","messageID":"msg_d7b830be10016FVbbGqDw5a8KX","sessionID":"ses_2847f2e74ffeGWPWz8Ke9vbXmV","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:26","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/test_spec.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/test_spec.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube 测试用例规范 (TDD Specification)\n2: \n3: 要求 AI 在实现业务代码时，同步完成以下测试用例，作为实现完成度的判定标准。\n4: \n5: ## 1. 核心控制器测试 (Workload Manager)\n6: - **TestCase-WM-001**: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口。输入合法 `AgentRuntime` 定义，预期返回 `200 OK` 及 `sessionId`。\n7: - **TestCase-WM-002**: 验证 Sandbox 幂等性。相同 `name` 连续调用两次，预期返回相同 `sessionId`。\n8: - **TestCase-WM-003**: 验证非法输入拦截。输入缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，预期返回 `400 Bad Request`。\n9: \n10: ## 2. 路由与会话测试 (Router)\n11: - **TestCase-RT-001**: 验证 Auth 拦截。未携带 Bearer Token 请求 `/v1/execute`，预期返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n12: - **TestCase-RT-002**: 验证会话路由。模拟 Redis 中存在会话，Router 成功将请求转发至后端（Mock 后端）。\n13: - **TestCase-RT-003**: 验证会话过期。模拟 Redis 中 Token 已失效，返回 `404 Not Found`。\n14: \n15: ## 3. 存储层测试 (Store)\n16: - **TestCase-ST-001**: Redis Set/Get 验证。成功存储并检索 `SessionInfo` 结构体。\n17: - **TestCase-ST-002**: 过期时间验证。验证 Key 携带正确的 TTL（默认 24h）。\n18: \n19: ## 4. 编码执行引擎测试 (PicoD)\n20: - **TestCase-PD-001**: Python 代码执行。发送 `print(\"hello\")`，预期 stdout 为 `hello\\n`，exitCode 为 0。\n21: - **TestCase-PD-002**: 错误处理。发送语法错误代码，预期 stderr 包含 `SyntaxError`。\n22: \n23: ## 5. Python SDK 测试\n24: - **TestCase-SDK-001**: 上下文管理器验证。使用 `with CodeInterpreterClient(...) as client:` 确保结束时自动调用 `close()`。\n25: - **TestCase-SDK-002**: 异常映射。服务端返回 500 时，SDK 抛出自定义 `AgentCubeError` 而非原始 HTTP 错误。\n26: \n27: ## 实施要求\n28: - **Go 代码**：必须位于对应的 `*_test.go` 中，可通过 `go test ./...` 运行。\n29: - **Python 代码**：必须位于 `tests/` 目录或 `test_*.py` 文件中，可通过 `pytest` 运行。\n\n(End of file - total 29 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube 测试用例规范 (TDD Specification)\n\n要求 AI 在实现业务代码时，同步完成以下测试用例，作为实现完成度的判定标准。\n\n## 1. 核心控制器测试 (Workload Manager)\n- **TestCase-WM-001**: 验证 Sandbox 创建接口。输入合法 `AgentRuntime` 定义，预期返回 `200 OK` 及 `sessionId`。\n- **TestCase-WM-002**: 验证 Sandbox 幂等性。相同 `name` 连续调用两次，预期返回相同 `sessionId`。\n- **TestCase-WM-003**: 验证非法输入拦截。输入缺失 `podTemplate` 的请求，预期返回 `400 Bad Request`。\n\n## 2. 路由与会话测试 (Router)\n- **TestCase-RT-001**: 验证 Auth 拦截。未携带 Bearer Token 请求 `/v1/execute`，预期返回 `401 Unauthorized`。\n- **TestCase-RT-002**: 验证会话路由。模拟 Redis 中存在会话，Router 成功将请求转发至后端（Mock 后端）。\n- **TestCase-RT-003**: 验证会话过期。模拟 Redis 中 Token 已失效，返回 `404 Not Found`。\n\n## 3. 存储层测试 (Store)\n- **TestCase-ST-001**: Redis Set/Get 验证。成功存储并检索 `SessionInfo` 结构体。\n- **TestCase-ST-002**: 过期时间验证。验证 Key 携带正确的 TTL（默认 24h）。\n\n## 4. 编码执行引擎测试 (PicoD)\n- **TestCase-PD-001**: Python 代码执行。发送 `print(\"hello\")`，预期 stdout 为 `hello\\n`，exitCode 为 0。","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/test_spec.md","time":{"start":1775893685922,"end":1775893685936}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775893685939,"sessionID":"ses_2847f2e74ffeGWPWz8Ke9vbXmV","part":{"id":"prt_d7b831c7d001nKl0dEm04UgWlJ","messageID":"msg_d7b830be10016FVbbGqDw5a8KX","sessionID":"ses_2847f2e74ffeGWPWz8Ke9vbXmV","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:27","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/VERIFICATION_REPORT.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/VERIFICATION_REPORT.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube Implementation Verification Report\n2: \n3: **AR:** AR-019 — CLI Binary Entry (4 binaries)  \n4: **Module:** cmd  \n5: **Language:** Go  \n6: **Date:** 2026-04-11  \n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Executive Summary\n11: \n12: | Component | Status | Notes |\n13: |-----------|--------|-------|\n14: | client-go Library | ❌ **MISSING** | Not implemented - required for CLI binaries |\n15: | cmd/agentd | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n16: | cmd/router | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n17: | cmd/workload-manager | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n18: | cmd/picod | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n19: | API Types (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1) | ✅ **IMPLEMENTED** | AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, Sandbox types defined |\n20: | Package Implementations | ✅ **IMPLEMENTED** | pkg/agentd, pkg/router, pkg/picod, pkg/workloadmanager |\n21: \n22: **Overall Status:** ❌ **NOT COMPLIANT** - Major gaps in required implementation\n23: \n24: ---\n25: \n26: ## Detailed Verification\n27: \n28: ### 1. Client-Go Library (deployment/client-go.md)\n29: \n30: **Spec Requirements:**\n31: - Module path: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n32: - API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n33: - Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n34: \n35: **Required Components:**\n36: \n37: | Component | Spec Location | Status | Notes |\n38: |-----------|---------------|--------|-------|\n39: | **Clientset Interface** | `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | ❌ Missing | Should expose `Discovery()`, `RuntimeV1alpha1()` |\n40: | **Clientset Constructors** | `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | ❌ Missing | 4 constructors required |\n41: | **Typed Client Interface** | `typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` | ❌ Missing | `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` |\n42: | **AgentRuntime Interface** | `typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | ❌ Missing | 10 CRUD methods + expansion |\n43: | **CodeInterpreter Interface** | `typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | ❌ Missing | Same pattern as AgentRuntime |\n44: | **Scheme Registration** | `clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go` | ❌ Missing | Scheme, Codecs, ParameterCodec |\n45: | **Fake Clientset** | `clientset/versioned/fake/` | ❌ Missing | For testing |\n46: | **SharedInformerFactory** | `informers/externalversions/factory.go` | ❌ Missing | With options, Start/Shutdown/WaitForCacheSync |\n47: | **Generic Informer** | `informers/externalversions/generic.go` | ❌ Missing | `ForResource()` routing |\n48: | **AgentRuntime Informer** | `informers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | ❌ Missing | |\n49: | **CodeInterpreter Informer** | `informers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | ❌ Missing | |\n50: | **AgentRuntime Lister** | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | ❌ Missing | Lister + NamespaceLister |\n51: | **CodeInterpreter Lister** | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | ❌ Missing | Lister + NamespaceLister |\n52: \n53: **Verification Command:**\n54: ```bash\n55: $ ls -la client-go/\n56: ls: cannot access 'client-go/': No such file or directory\n57: ```\n58: \n59: **Status:** ❌ **CRITICAL GAP** - The client-go library is completely missing. This is a foundational dependency for the CLI binaries.\n60: \n61: ---\n62: \n63: ### 2. CLI Binaries (cmd/)\n64: \n65: **Spec Requirements:** 4 binaries as defined in `cmd/design.md`\n66: \n67: #### 2.1 cmd/agentd\n68: \n69: **Expected:** `cmd/agentd/main.go` (~80 lines)\n70: - Idle cleanup controller entry point\n71: - Imports: `pkg/agentd`, `client-go`\n72: - Configuration: Kubeconfig, SyncPeriod, GracefulTimeout\n73: - Creates controller-runtime manager\n74: - Starts AgentRuntime reconciler\n75: \n76: **Actual:**\n77: ```bash\n78: $ ls -la cmd/agentd/\n79: total 8\n80: drwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 Apr 11 12:14 .\n81: drwxr-xr-x 6 root root 4096 Apr 11 13:03 ..\n82: ```\n83: \n84: **Status:** ❌ **MISSING** - Directory exists but empty\n85: \n86: ---\n87: \n88: #### 2.2 cmd/router\n89: \n90: **Expected:** `cmd/router/main.go` (~100 lines)\n91: - Session routing proxy entry point\n92: - Imports: `pkg/router`, `pkg/store`, `client-go`\n93: - Configuration: Port, Debug, RedisAddr, WorkloadManagerURL, GracefulTimeout\n94: - Initializes Gin HTTP server\n95: - Sets up JWT middleware\n96: \n97: **Actual:**\n98: ```bash\n99: $ ls -la cmd/router/\n100: total 8\n101: drwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 Apr 11 06:01 .\n102: drwxr-xr-x 6 root root 4096 Apr 11 13:03 ..\n103: ```\n104: \n105: **Status:** ❌ **MISSING** - Directory exists but empty\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: #### 2.3 cmd/workload-manager\n110: \n111: **Expected:** `cmd/workload-manager/main.go` (~120 lines)\n112: - Sandbox orchestration entry point\n113: - Imports: `pkg/workloadmanager`, `client-go`\n114: - Configuration: Port, Kubeconfig, RedisAddr, DefaultImage, Namespace, GracefulTimeout\n115: - Creates controller-runtime manager\n116: - Starts CodeInterpreter controller + HTTP API server\n117: \n118: **Actual:**\n119: ```bash\n120: $ ls -la cmd/workload-manager/\n121: total 8\n122: drwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 Apr 11 04:21 .\n123: drwxr-xr-x 6 root root 4096 Apr 11 13:03 ..\n124: ```\n125: \n126: **Status:** ❌ **MISSING** - Directory exists but empty\n127: \n128: ---\n129: \n130: #### 2.4 cmd/picod\n131: \n132: **Expected:** `cmd/picod/main.go` (~90 lines)\n133: - Sandbox daemon entry point\n134: - Imports: `pkg/picod`\n135: - Configuration: Port, Workspace, ReadHeaderTimeout\n136: - Initializes workspace\n137: - Starts HTTP server\n138: \n139: **Actual:**\n140: ```bash\n141: $ ls -la cmd/picod/\n142: total 8\n143: drwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 Apr 11 13:03 .\n144: drwxr-xr-x 6 root root 4096 Apr 11 13:03 ..\n145: ```\n146: \n147: **Status:** ❌ **MISSING** - Directory exists but empty\n148: \n149: ---\n150: \n151: ### 3. API Types (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1)\n152: \n153: **Verification:** API types are correctly defined\n154: \n155: | Type | File | Status | Notes |\n156: |------|------|--------|-------|\n157: | `AgentRuntime` | `agentruntime_types.go` | ✅ | Complete with Spec, Status, Conditions |\n158: | `AgentRuntimeList` | `agentruntime_types.go` | ✅ | Standard Kubernetes list type |\n159: | `CodeInterpreter` | `codeinterpreter_types.go` | ✅ | Complete with Spec, Status, Conditions |\n160: | `CodeInterpreterList` | `codeinterpreter_types.go` | ✅ | Standard Kubernetes list type |\n161: | `Sandbox` | `sandbox_types.go` | ✅ | Present (not in spec but implemented) |\n162: | `SchemeGroupVersion` | `register.go` | ✅ | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` |\n163: \n164: **Key Verification Points:**\n165: - ✅ Group version: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n166: - ✅ Resource plural: `agentruntimes` (from kubebuilder annotation)\n167: - ✅ Resource plural: `codeinterpreters` (from kubebuilder annotation)\n168: - ✅ `+genclient` markers present on types\n169: - ✅ `+k8s:deepcopy-gen` markers present\n170: \n171: ---\n172: \n173: ### 4. Package Implementations (pkg/)\n174: \n175: | Package | Status | Notes |\n176: |---------|--------|-------|\n177: | `pkg/agentd` | ✅ | Reconciler implementation present |\n178: | `pkg/router` | ✅ | JWT, handlers, middleware present |\n179: | `pkg/picod` | ✅ | Sandbox daemon implementation present |\n180: | `pkg/workloadmanager` | ✅ | Controller, service, types present |\n181: | `pkg/store` | ✅ | Redis/Valkey store implementation |\n182: | `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` | ✅ | API types with deepcopy generation |\n183: \n184: ---\n185: \n186: ## Dependency Analysis\n187: \n188: ### Go Module (go.mod)\n189: \n190: **Status:** ✅ Present and correctly configured\n191: \n192: **Key Dependencies:**\n193: - `k8s.io/client-go v0.32.0` ✅\n194: - `k8s.io/api v0.32.0` ✅\n195: - `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.32.0` ✅\n196: - `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.19.0` ✅\n197: \n198: **Missing Dependency:**\n199: - `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` ❌ - This should be a local submodule or internal package\n200: \n201: ---\n202: \n203: ## Test Status\n204: \n205: ```\n206: ok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd    (cached)\n207: ok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1       (cached)\n208: ok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/picod/jwt (cached)\n209: ok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store     (cached)\n210: ```\n211: \n212: **Note:** Tests pass for existing packages, but there are many packages with `[no test files]`. This is acceptable for the `cmd/` binaries as they are thin wrappers, but the client-go library would need comprehensive tests.\n213: \n214: ---\n215: \n216: ## Build Verification\n217: \n218: ```bash\n219: $ go build ./...\n220: # Success - no errors\n221: ```\n222: \n223: **Note:** Build succeeds because the missing `client-go` and `cmd/*` are not imported by existing code. The design documents reference them, but the actual import statements don't exist.\n224: \n225: ---\n226: \n227: ## Compliance Matrix\n228: \n229: | Requirement | Spec Location | Implementation | Status |\n230: |-------------|---------------|----------------|--------|\n231: | Clientset Interface | client-go.md:19-22 | Missing | ❌ |\n232: | Clientset Constructors | client-go.md:29-34 | Missing | ❌ |\n233: | RuntimeV1alpha1Interface | client-go.md:44-49 | Missing | ❌ |\n234: | AgentRuntimeInterface | client-go.md:61-72 | Missing | ❌ |\n235: | CodeInterpreterInterface | client-go.md:79 | Missing | ❌ |\n236: | Scheme Registration | client-go.md:96-101 | Missing | ❌ |\n237: | SharedInformerFactory | client-go.md:109-127 | Missing | ❌ |\n238: | AgentRuntime Informer | client-go.md:152-158 | Missing | ❌ |\n239: | AgentRuntime Lister | client-go.md:184-199 | Missing | ❌ |\n240: | Fake Clientset | client-go.md:210-217 | Missing | ❌ |\n241: | cmd/agentd/main.go | cmd/design.md:125 | Missing | ❌ |\n242: | cmd/router/main.go | cmd/design.md:127 | Missing | ❌ |\n243: | cmd/workload-manager/main.go | cmd/design.md:129 | Missing | ❌ |\n244: | cmd/picod/main.go | cmd/design.md:131 | Missing | ❌ |\n245: | API Types | pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 | Present | ✅ |\n246: \n247: ---\n248: \n249: ## Blockers for Completion\n250: \n251: 1. **client-go Library Generation** (P0 - Critical)\n252:    - Must generate typed clients for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n253:    - Requires code-generator or manual implementation\n254:    - Blocks all Kubernetes-dependent binaries\n255: \n256: 2. **Binary Implementation** (P0 - Critical)\n257:    - Each binary needs main.go with:\n258:      - Flag parsing\n259:      - Configuration validation\n260:      - Dependency initialization\n261:      - Graceful shutdown handling\n262:      - Service startup\n263: \n264: ---\n265: \n266: ## Recommendations\n267: \n268: ### Option 1: Generate client-go using code-generator\n269: 1. Add `k8s.io/code-generator` to tools\n270: 2. Create `hack/update-codegen.sh` script\n271: 3. Run generation to create client-go/ directory\n272: 4. Implement cmd/* binaries using generated client\n273: \n274: ### Option 2: Manual client-go implementation\n275: 1. Implement typed clients manually\n276: 2. Create clientset, informers, listers as per spec\n277: 3. More work but complete control over implementation\n278: \n279: ### Option 3: Use controller-runtime client directly\n280: 1. Skip client-go generation\n281: 2. Use `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client` in binaries\n282: 3. Simpler but deviates from spec\n283: \n284: ---\n285: \n286: ## Conclusion\n287: \n288: The **AR-019 CLI Binary Entry** implementation is **NOT COMPLIANT** with the specification. While the underlying package implementations (`pkg/*`) and API types are complete, the critical deliverables are missing:\n289: \n290: 1. The `client-go` library is entirely absent - this is a foundational requirement\n291: 2. All 4 CLI binary entry points (`cmd/*`) are empty directories\n292: \n293: To achieve compliance, the client-go library must be generated (or manually implemented) following the exact structure specified in `deployment/client-go.md`, and then the 4 CLI binaries must be implemented as thin wrappers around the existing `pkg/*` implementations.\n294: \n295: **Estimated Remaining Work:**\n296: - client-go generation: ~4-6 hours\n297: - cmd/* binary implementation: ~2-3 hours each (8-12 hours total)\n298: - Testing and integration: ~4 hours\n299: - **Total: ~16-22 hours**\n300: \n301: ---\n302: \n303: *Report generated by quality-gate verification process*\n\n(End of file - total 303 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube Implementation Verification Report\n\n**AR:** AR-019 — CLI Binary Entry (4 binaries)  \n**Module:** cmd  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Date:** 2026-04-11  \n\n---\n\n## Executive Summary\n\n| Component | Status | Notes |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| client-go Library | ❌ **MISSING** | Not implemented - required for CLI binaries |\n| cmd/agentd | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n| cmd/router | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n| cmd/workload-manager | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n| cmd/picod | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n| API Types (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1) | ✅ **IMPLEMENTED** | AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, Sandbox types defined |\n| Package Implementations | ✅ **IMPLEMENTED** | pkg/agentd, pkg/router, pkg/picod, pkg/workloadmanager |","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/ope