\n- Runtime and service imports functional\n\n### Detailed Report\n\nI've written a complete verification report to:\n**`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/VERIFICATION_REPORT_AR023.md`**\n\nThe report includes:\n- Complete compliance matrix (all 21 requirements)\n- Detailed command parameter verification\n- Runtime class method verification\n- Service method verification\n- Dependency verification\n- Functional test results\n\n### Conclusion\n\nThe implementation **meets all requirements** for AR-023. The invoke and status commands are fully functional with proper error handling, provider abstraction (agentcube/k8s), and rich CLI output formatting.","time":{"start":1775894113900,"end":1775894113900}}}
